<h1 class="headline">Your verification code</h1>
<p class="subheadline">Use this one-time code to {{purpose}} your {{companyName}} account.</p>

<p class="text">Hello,</p>
<p class="text">Enter the code below in the app to continue. For your security, the code expires in {{expiryMinutes}} minutes.</p>

<div class="panel">
    <div class="code-label center">One-time password</div>
    <div class="code">{{otp}}</div>
    <div class="meta">Valid for {{expiryMinutes}} minutes</div>
</div>

<div class="notice warning">
    <strong>Security notice:</strong> Never share this code with anyone. {{companyName}} staff will never ask for your OTP.
</div>

<p class="text">If you did not request this code, you can ignore this message.</p>
